jobs.name: Hourly System Backup to Google Drive

payload.message: Run the backup script: bash /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/backup-to-gdrive.sh — Report the backup name, location, and size. If it fails, report the error.

Podcast episode mining. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/podcast-clip-miner/SKILL.md. Mine latest AI Agents Podcast episodes for building blocks: paradoxes, quotes, problems, arcs. Output 9 building block categories + content ideas. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/episode-mining-YYYY-MM-DD.md

B-roll suggestions. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/broll-brian/SKILL.md. Check for upcoming video scripts in /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/. Generate specific B-roll footage suggestions with AI image generator prompts. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/broll-suggestions-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Content scheduler run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/contentstudio-scheduler/SKILL.md. Queue approved content from /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/ for publication. Check platform-specific char limits and optimal posting times. Save schedule to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/content-schedule-YYYY-MM-DD.md
Dashboard data refresh. Count current cron jobs, check agent health, log to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/dashboard-data.json with timestamp, cron count, agent status.

Grain Task Orchestrator run. Use mcporter to call grain.list_attended_meetings to find meetings from today. For each meeting, fetch transcript via grain.fetch_meeting_transcript and notes via grain.fetch_meeting_notes. Extract action items and create Todoist tasks using mcporter todoist.add-tasks. Follow the methodology in /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/grain-task-orchestrator/SKILL.md. Map speakers to team members where possible. Only process meetings from today.

Nightly improvement analysis. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/recursive-improvement-protocol/SKILL.md. Review today's agent activity: cron job success/failure rates, task completion, cost tracking. Identify top 3 improvement opportunities. Save proposals to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/improvement-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Model monitor run. Check OpenRouter for new or updated AI models. Compare against current model ladder (Grok 4.1 Fast, Gemini 3 Pro, Sonnet 4.5, Opus 4.6). If better options exist, generate a config.patch proposal. Check pricing changes. Save findings to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace-openclaw-builder/memory/model-updates-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Morning improvement apply. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/recursive-improvement-protocol/SKILL.md. Check /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/ for last night's improvement-analysis file. Review proposals and apply any that are low-risk and high-impact. Update MEMORY.md with changes made. Save log to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/improvement-apply-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Trend Scout daily run. Search for today's top AI news using web_search. Filter through Rise Productive's lens: practical automation, enterprise AI, agent frameworks, workflow tools. Skip consumer AI, art drama, AGI speculation. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/idea-irving/SKILL.md and /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/creator-trend-tracker/SKILL.md for methodology. Output 3-5 content opportunities with headlines, angles, and hooks. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/trend-scan-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Social Writer daily run. Read today's trend scan at /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/ (latest trend-scan file). Pick the best content opportunity and write ONE LinkedIn post in Demetri Panici's voice. Read these skills: /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/copywriting-cam/SKILL.md, /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/person-pete/references/blacklist.md, /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/hook-harry/SKILL.md, /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/work-worth-doing/SKILL.md. Run full blacklist check, self-score, iterate if below 7. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/linkedin-post-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Morning briefing for Demetri. Pull today's Todoist tasks across all team projects (Internal Content, External Content, AI Consulting, Paid Ads, Rise Operations, Sales & Growth). Summarize what's due today, flag overdue items, note any P1/P2 priorities. Keep it concise — bullet points, no fluff. Use mcporter call todoist.find-tasks-by-date with startDate=today.

Daily CRM review. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/daily-crm-orchestrator/SKILL.md. Review pipeline across Instantly and LinkedIn. Flag stale leads, suggest next actions. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/crm-review-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Shorts Scripter run. Write ONE YouTube Shorts script (30-45 sec). Search for a trending AI topic, then read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/shorts-hook-looper/SKILL.md and /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/funny-fran/SKILL.md. Write with: hook (first 2 sec pattern interrupt), body (insight), loop point (makes viewer rewatch). Run through /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/person-pete/references/blacklist.md. Self-score 1-10. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/shorts-script-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Paid Ads Monitor daily run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/paid-ads-reporting/SKILL.md. Check ad spend, performance metrics, budget pacing across all active campaigns (Arcade.dev Google/LinkedIn/Meta, Melanie). Flag anomalies (spend >120% of daily budget, CTR drops >20%, CPC spikes). Output a summary with: total spend today, performance by client, any flags. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/paid-ads-check-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Sponsor inbox check. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/sponsor-management/SKILL.md. Check hello@riseproductive.com for sponsor inquiries, track billing status, flag upsell opportunities. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/sponsor-inbox-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Podcast inbox check. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/ai-agents-podcast-ops/SKILL.md. Check for new guest inquiries, qualify against criteria (must deliver AI-related services). Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/podcast-inbox-YYYY-MM-DD.md

LinkedIn engagement run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/influencer-monitor/SKILL.md. Find high-value posts to engage with. Draft 3-5 thoughtful comments in Demetri's voice. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/linkedin-engagement-YYYY-MM-DD.md

LinkedIn connection review. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/linkedin-connection-qualifier/SKILL.md. Review pending connection requests, score for client potential and strategic value. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/linkedin-connections-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Outreach monitor run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/outreach-orchestrator/SKILL.md. Check Instantly campaign status, flag replies needing attention, monitor bounce rates. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/outreach-monitor-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Social graphics generation. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/rise-visuals/SKILL.md. Generate social media graphics for the week's planned content. Use typography-first design system. Save concepts to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/graphics-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Blog Writer weekly run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/rise-blog/SKILL.md for the 14-category QA methodology. Pick a topic from the week's trend scans in /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/. Write a 1000-1500 word blog post in Demetri's voice. Run through /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/person-pete/references/blacklist.md. Include SEO meta description. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/blog-draft-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Thumbnail Designer run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/rise-youtube-thumbnails/SKILL.md. Research the latest video topic from the trend scans in /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/. Analyze competitor thumbnails. Generate thumbnail concept with: text overlay suggestion, color scheme, composition notes, expression/pose guidance for Demetri. If mcp-image is available via mcporter, generate an actual thumbnail image. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/thumbnail-concept-YYYY-MM-DD.md

YouTube Comment Responder. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/influencer-monitor/SKILL.md. Check Rise Productive YouTube channel for recent comments. Draft engagement-optimized replies in Demetri's voice (direct, kind, helpful — not corporate). Prioritize: questions, thoughtful comments, potential leads. Skip: spam, generic 'great video'. Output drafted replies to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/youtube-comments-YYYY-MM-DD.md for Demetri to review before posting.

Podcast guest outreach. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/outreach-orchestrator/SKILL.md in podcast mode. Find potential AI Agents Podcast guests. Research backgrounds, draft outreach messages. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/guest-outreach-YYYY-MM-DD.md

SEO blog review. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/rise-blog/SKILL.md. Review recently published blogs for SEO improvements: meta descriptions, keyword density, internal linking opportunities. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/seo-review-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Clip extraction run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/clip-catcher/SKILL.md. Find best 30-90s clips from recent long-form content. Score using 4-factor system (standalone clarity, hook strength, emotional intensity, actionability). Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/clip-extraction-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Todoist hygiene audit. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/todoist-project-manager/SKILL.md. Audit all team projects for: stale tasks (>7 days no update), missing descriptions, overdue items, unassigned tasks. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/todoist-audit-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Client upsell check. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/ai-hormozi/SKILL.md. Review active clients (Arcade.dev, Jotform, Melanie) for upsell opportunities. Use Hormozi methodology for value-based proposals. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/upsell-check-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Meeting content mining. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/meeting-clip-miner/SKILL.md. Use Grain MCP to fetch this week's meeting transcripts. Extract building blocks: paradoxes, client problems, success stories, quotable moments. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/meeting-mining-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Ad performance report. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/paid-ads-reporting/SKILL.md. Generate weekly performance reports for all active ad campaigns (Arcade.dev Google/LinkedIn/Meta, Melanie). Include spend, conversions, CPA, ROAS. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/ad-report-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Friday improvement review. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/recursive-improvement-protocol/SKILL.md. Review the week's agent activity: check what tasks were completed in Jerry's World Todoist project (6g26XRJq6hmwpvCq), identify any blocked items, and propose improvements. Write a summary to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/memory/weekly-review-YYYY-WW.md. Keep it actionable — what worked, what didn't, what to change next week.

Weekly content calendar planning. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/content-orchestrator/SKILL.md. Plan the week's content across LinkedIn, Twitter, YouTube, blog, newsletter. Map content to trend scans from /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/content-calendar-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Run the weekly AI newsletter research for Rise Productive. 1) Search for the top 5 AI news stories from the past week using web_search. 2) Read the skill file at /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/ai-weekly-newsletter/SKILL.md for methodology. 3) Filter stories through Demetri's 'Work Worth Doing' lens — focus on practical AI automation, not hype. 4) Output a structured newsletter draft with: headline, 3-5 stories with Demetri-voice commentary, and a video outline suggestion. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/newsletter-draft-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Deep influencer scan. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/influencer-monitor/SKILL.md. Scan all 23 tracked influencers across LinkedIn, Twitter, YouTube. Score content with 4-factor system. Identify content gaps and trending topics. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/influencer-scan-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Lead Magnet Creator monthly run. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/content-orchestrator/SKILL.md. Create a new lead magnet concept for Rise Productive. This month's angle should come from the most popular content topics of the past 30 days (check trend scans in output/). Output: title, outline (5-7 sections), target audience, distribution plan, landing page copy draft. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/lead-magnet-YYYY-MM.md

Ad copy refresh. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/paid-ads-copywriting/SKILL.md. Review active ad campaigns for Arcade.dev and Melanie. Draft refreshed ad copy variants. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/ad-copy-refresh-YYYY-MM-DD.md

Monthly client ROI report. Read /Users/demetripanici/.agents/skills/paid-ads-reporting/SKILL.md. Generate comprehensive monthly ROI reports for all active clients (Arcade.dev, Jotform, Melanie). Include month-over-month trends, recommendations. Save to /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/workspace/output/monthly-roi-YYYY-MM.md

findings.title: Attack surface summary
findings.detail:
groups: open=0, allowlist=1
tools.elevated: enabled
hooks.webhooks: disabled
hooks.internal: disabled
browser control: enabled

findings.title: Reverse proxy headers are not trusted
findings.detail: gateway.bind is loopback and gateway.trustedProxies is empty. If you expose the Control UI through a reverse proxy, configure trusted proxies so local-client checks cannot be spoofed.
findings.remediation: Set gateway.trustedProxies to your proxy IPs or keep the Control UI local-only.

findings.title: Credentials dir is readable by others
findings.detail: /Users/demetripanici/.openclaw/credentials mode=755; credentials and allowlists can be sensitive.
